    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >官方游戏交流群 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >199271874</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不测星域是在宇宙中移动的星域。星域内的星球之间有传送通道连接，通过传送通道可以穿梭在星球之间。不测星域在移动的过程中，有时候会把一些新的星球传送进入自身体系。传送的过程中会平衡星球的能量。因此，在星系群中的各类星球上，无论文明是科技还是魔法，剑抑或枪炮、机甲，都能彼此一争高下。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家的星球遭遇到异星球敌人入侵。危机时，不测星域来临，玩家和敌人一起被打乱传送到了不测星域。玩家在新的星球上和新伙伴组成一个基地，努力生存下去。一边收集资源生产消耗品和武器装备，一边进行探索和战斗，誓要在新世界打败入侵者，找到回家的方向。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以组建多支队伍 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >冒险时玩家同一时间只能控制一支队伍，但是多支队伍能同时加入战斗，有时这也是必要的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389900/extras/ba455839ece8827202c6c6b9771f6091.poster.avif?t=1756395742\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389900/extras/ba455839ece8827202c6c6b9771f6091.webm?t=1756395742\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389900/extras/ba455839ece8827202c6c6b9771f6091.mp4?t=1756395742\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >守住要塞/基地 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >合理组织队伍进行防守和探险 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >咖啡馆 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >要塞/基地内经营咖啡馆。冒险家们在这里休息和集结。基于咖啡馆也有少量的采集和生产玩法。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战斗方式 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >较快速的战棋战斗方式，敌我盟军拥各自的行动冷却，战斗速度快，参战人数多，地形复杂，局势多变。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >重型武器</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >机甲炮塔都上场，能量平衡的缘故，强度有限。但是依然有优势。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389900/extras/1822d1c71b57cd525ace9ab144f8c074.poster.avif?t=1756395742\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389900/extras/1822d1c71b57cd525ace9ab144f8c074.webm?t=1756395742\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2389900/extras/1822d1c71b57cd525ace9ab144f8c074.mp4?t=1756395742\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
